            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="269428842">
            这是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>三天的行程图，几乎横跨了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>城，如果没有地陪作伴的话，以公共交通代步并不推荐这条线路。<br />
因为开车去香山会方便些，虽然堵，但回程的时候不用与游客等一班迟迟不来的公交还是很值得的。<br />
另外，雪花作为地道的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>妞儿，她知道哪里的小吃最地道，有选择自然就选择最好的了，所以有时我们为了寻家店铺扰些路……<br />
<br />

        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="269508573">
            本篇采用双人续写的游记模式，以我为主导，游记脉络顺序和主要文字由我来完成，雪花会开辟❄️雪花说❄️以一个地道<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>妞的角度来补充我没有完善的部分和吐槽我的夸张描写<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/30@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />更为客观地为大家介绍我俩眼中的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>城。
        </p>
            <div data-seq="267039050" data-index="1" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <img src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/27/3D/wKgBZ1oRii-AAQ2xAABMsfAgbBk849.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fh%2F150%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" class="no_word _j_anchor" title="食在北京" alt="食在北京" />
            </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_266951369" data-seq="266951390" data-pid="266951369" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8002059/266951369.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/7E/wKgBZ1oRSXGAG6apAAiSrVMM7WI78.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/7E/wKgBZ1oRSXGAG6apAAiSrVMM7WI78.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="266951369" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" target="_blank" class="_j_anchor">
                    <i class="house"></i>北京
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="266988235">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;△&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;日坛涮肉(日坛东路店)<br />
地址：日坛东路9号(日坛公园东侧，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10182.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="印度" target="_blank">印度</a>大使馆对面)<br />
营业时间：&nbsp;10:00-21:30&nbsp;<br />
由于“东来顺”<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>本土人并不推荐，咨询了在帝都多年的同学，推荐了这家以<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/62859.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="景泰" target="_blank">景泰</a>蓝包边的小铜火锅，那是来<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>的第一顿晚餐，从<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10099.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="上海" target="_blank">上海</a>到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>6个小时的火车早已使我饥肠辘辘，虽然只有一个人，但上图除了那盆生菜，确实都塞了下去。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_266951370" data-seq="266951391" data-pid="266951370" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8002059/266951370.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/7F/wKgBZ1oRSXKAG2EaAAXUMhLsM5E42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/7F/wKgBZ1oRSXKAG2EaAAXUMhLsM5E42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="266951370" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" target="_blank" class="_j_anchor">
                    <i class="house"></i>北京
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="266990179">
            这里的火锅好像不时兴自己调制酱料，点了麻酱（太淡，后来要要了点盐自己调了下味道就好很多了，可能我从小口味重吧）还有小水萝卜、糖蒜（好吃！）、花生、葱花儿、香菜碟子。还是很怀念在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10122.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="英国" target="_blank">英国</a>读书那会儿，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>同学自己用芝麻酱韭菜花儿调制的火锅料。值得一提的是北冰洋汽水儿，这个<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10099.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="上海" target="_blank">上海</a>真没有，有一股小时候瓶装汽水的味道，很是怀念。<br />

        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="269512103">
            ❄️雪花说❄️作为土生土长的local，当别人问起来<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>吃火锅，第一介绍的就是老<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>铜锅～清汤，涮羊肉，外加芝麻酱，豆腐乳，韭菜花，香菜，葱合成的蘸料，那滋味简直了～！<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>的东来顺可以说是各大游客到京必去餐厅推荐，但说实话，真心觉得不好吃啊，老店的传承没做好，要接受群众的批评！<br />
糖蒜真的是我的心头好，每次吃火锅不吃点糖蒜心里都痒痒，而且吃完了嘴里不会有像生蒜余留的重口味。<br />
着重来讲一下北冰洋！北冰洋我真的是人见人推，我一个从不喝碳酸饮料的人，对北冰洋欲罢不能！北冰洋作为国货之光，无论在炎热的夏季配烤串，还是在寒冷的冬季配火锅都是绝佳的搭配！墙裂！推荐来<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>的人儿们尝试一下！不好喝你找我<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/25@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_266951365" data-seq="266951386" data-pid="266951365" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8002059/266951365.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/7B/wKgBZ1oRSW2AH5s9AAfjYr5AMyU36.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/7B/wKgBZ1oRSW2AH5s9AAfjYr5AMyU36.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="266951365" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" target="_blank" class="_j_anchor">
                    <i class="house"></i>北京
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="266984161">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;△&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;四季民福烤鸭店(前门大栅栏店)<br />
地址：前门大栅栏商业街18号(1796商场二层，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10602.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="同仁" target="_blank">同仁</a>堂东侧)<br />
营业时间：&nbsp;周一至周日&nbsp;10:30-22:00<br />
由于“全聚德”<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>本土人也不推荐，那“四季民福”可以说是吃<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>烤鸭最权威的店了，整个烤至过程你清晰可见，师傅片鸭的过程也可以当表演来欣赏。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_266951366" data-seq="266951387" data-pid="266951366" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8002059/266951366.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/7C/wKgBZ1oRSW6ADOp2AAWKYfAXB1A41.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/7C/wKgBZ1oRSW6ADOp2AAWKYfAXB1A41.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="266951366" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" target="_blank" class="_j_anchor">
                    <i class="house"></i>北京
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="269511972">
            上的第一盘是鸭肉与鸭皮分开吃的，鸭皮蘸白糖，鸭肉蘸蒜泥，有别于传统卷饼吃法，个人认为鸭皮蘸白糖这种吃法又新颖又好吃，有入口即化的感觉。但对蒜泥接受不能，只是略微尝试了一下。<br />
等到第二盘上桌，其实与第一盘无异，只是用传统卷饼吃，因为鸭皮较外面馆子里的更为脆嫩，鸭肉也恰到好处，涂上蘸酱、配上韧劲十足的卷饼与黄瓜大葱丝，的确配得上京城性价比最高的头衔。<br />

        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="266985831">
            ❄️雪花说❄️&nbsp;人人都道来<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>吃烤鸭，见得最多的竟然就是前门，南锣鼓巷卖的20元一份的“片皮鸭”说真的，各位看官们，别买！你要买了吃了说<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>烤鸭不好吃，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>烤鸭会说这个锅我不背！四季民福的烤鸭是我觉得性价比很高的烤鸭，好吃便宜，人也不多，强推！额外再介绍几个地儿：1.利群烤鸭店。这个真的第二强推，排第二因为地儿有点不好找，在前门一个胡<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10435.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="同里" target="_blank">同里</a>，建议步行过去。但酒香不怕巷子深啊，这家店真真好吃绝了，有时间的一定要去试试，而且超级多政要明星都去过这家店非常的出名。2.全聚德。这个全国人民都知道的吧，前门总店门口人山人海的排队，人多的时候不单点，只卖套餐，略黑，味道还是不错的，毕竟名气在这儿啊！3.大董烤鸭店。讲究文艺范儿，环境，贵的人，那你选这家店没错！4.便宜坊。性价比高，但烤鸭水平层次不齐，比较容易踩雷！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_266951372" data-seq="266951393" data-pid="266951372" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8002059/266951372.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/82/wKgBZ1oRSXSAN6JAAA6aMtoovYo23.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/82/wKgBZ1oRSXSAN6JAAA6aMtoovYo23.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="266951372" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" target="_blank" class="_j_anchor">
                    <i class="house"></i>北京
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="266991757">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;△&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;芦月轩羊蝎子(管庄店)<br />
地址：管庄东里<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>建材研究总院院内<br />
营业时间：&nbsp;周一至周日&nbsp;11：00-22:00&nbsp;<br />
来了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>城，羊蝎子自然也是不能错过的，记得那时候在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10122.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="英国" target="_blank">英国</a>也是由<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>的同学推荐吃了羊蝎子，不知为什么这种在外国人眼中的下脚料总能在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>人手中发挥出它最大的价值，既有骨又有肉，骨头能把汤的鲜味吊出来，肉又在骨缝之间，需要人去嘶咬方能食其味，个中趣味想想也能令人食指大动。<br />
他家羊蝎子分量足，两三人一小锅足矣，肉炖得“很烂”，骨髓也“多”，再加点素菜，丸子，得撑个“肚歪”才能出来。<br />

        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="269511074">
            ❄️雪花说❄️&nbsp;这家店是我爱吃羊蝎子的朋友强烈推荐给我的，特意找了总店让我去吃。我们晚上9:30到的，三下五除二点了一大桌子，整体感觉分量极大，注意别踩雷，别点大白菜！一大盘子白菜根子让你怀疑人生！另外停车真的无敌便宜了，2个小时1块钱，超值！<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>好多分店，选离你最近的就行。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_266951374" data-seq="266951395" data-pid="266951374" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8002059/266951374.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/84/wKgBZ1oRSXaAc6wGAAS6NegWIIE17.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/84/wKgBZ1oRSXaAc6wGAAS6NegWIIE17.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="266951374" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" target="_blank" class="_j_anchor">
                    <i class="house"></i>北京
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="266960894">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;△&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;小吊梨汤(香山店)<br />
地址：香山买卖街东口(近香山5号停车场商业配套楼)<br />
营业时间：&nbsp;周一至周日&nbsp;11:00-15:00&nbsp;17:00-21:30&nbsp;<br />
小吊梨汤是雪花在香山无意中找到的一家京菜馆儿，比较有特色的是他家的装修，两层的木楼“古色古香”，花花草草、红灯笼、招贴画、蝈蝈……应有尽有。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_266951375" data-seq="266951396" data-pid="266951375" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8002059/266951375.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/84/wKgBZ1oRSXeAaJkIAAPAMmKJiOI42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/84/wKgBZ1oRSXeAaJkIAAPAMmKJiOI42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="266951375" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" target="_blank" class="_j_anchor">
                    <i class="house"></i>北京
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="266959325">
            角角落落都透着“老<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>的味儿”。菜单是“两盒小木牌”，“想吃哪个翻过来便是”。干酪鱼“精致可人”，“细腻爽滑”；梨汤“清淡”，小吊壶煞是“可爱”。总体来说这家店胜在貌不在味，不予评价。<br />

        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="269510355">
            ❄️雪花说❄️小吊梨汤啊小吊梨汤，名副其实，必点的小吊梨汤真的好喝，但是如果不喜欢浓稠口感的朋友，别点啊！喝的时候就感觉口口精华，唯一不满足的就是杯子太小了，一口一杯，急坏我们这些放荡不羁的少女了！干酪鱼作为餐后甜点非常的好吃，甜度适中，口感似果冻！当然了牛腩炖饭就别点了，肯定没咱妈做的好吃！整体感觉就是咸咸的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>菜，冲梨汤我下次也不会再去了(捂脸小蜂)
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_266951376" data-seq="266951397" data-pid="266951376" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8002059/266951376.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/85/wKgBZ1oRSXiAFVb1AAWH_A1sJdU78.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/85/wKgBZ1oRSXiAFVb1AAWH_A1sJdU78.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="266951376" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" target="_blank" class="_j_anchor">
                    <i class="house"></i>北京
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="267180807">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;△<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;姚记炒肝店(簋街店)&nbsp;<br />
地址：东直门内大街288-3号(北新桥十字路口东南角)<br />
营业时间：&nbsp;周一至周日&nbsp;06:00-23:00&nbsp;<br />
说到炒肝儿，那得是姚记。姚记炒肝儿早已是名声在外，这是老<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>吃早点的地儿，点上一碗炒肝儿，一盘灌肠儿，再来个炸酥肉。就能体味一下啥叫自在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>味儿。他们家炒肝儿弄得干净，没啥大肠味儿，灌肠蘸蒜泥吃还行，酥肉口味略淡。簋街上还有有名的胡大，当然啦，他们家的队看不到头也是真的。<br />

        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="269510182">
            ❄️雪花说❄️冬天，一碗热腾腾的炒肝就着两口包子，喜欢吃蒜的再来碗蒜，吃上一口，那感觉真真舒坦！真别说，姚记炒肝真和别的店不一样，汤汁勾芡的的很浓郁，炒肝儿不仅嫩还不腥！好吃到家了！！其他的我都觉得一般，不做评价了！<br />
胡大小龙虾顺便提一句，好吃是真的，贵也是真的，但是好吃也不能上天对吧，前面要是有几百号人排队等着咱大冷天别在那执着了<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/24@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_267180810" data-seq="267180811" data-pid="267180810" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8002059/267180810.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/7E/13/wKgBZ1oScP2ALFl5AALtX9fCUTY92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/7E/13/wKgBZ1oScP2ALFl5AALtX9fCUTY92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="267180810" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" target="_blank" class="_j_anchor">
                    <i class="house"></i>北京
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="267001178">
            萝卜丝，黄瓜丝，黄豆，京酱，与过了凉水的面条一起就组成了一碗地地道道的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>炸酱面，简单的搭配却彰显着劳动人民无限的智慧（好吧，这不是舌尖），这家姚记的面条并没有过凉水，所以拌的时候面条会有点坨，使得吃到最后吃口很咸。<br />

        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="269510050">
            ❄️雪花说❄️&nbsp;对于我来说，炸酱面好不好吃就两个点，1.面条筋不劲道。2.面条过没过凉水！这太重要了，有了这两点，其他都是次要的！！好多人觉得<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>炸酱面一般，都在于觉得面条是一大坨，口感不好，配料也没什么可吃的！所以到店，你们可以跟服务员提一嘴儿，要求面条过个凉水，要再不好吃，你就打他！<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/25@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_266951380" data-seq="266951401" data-pid="266951380" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8002059/266951380.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/8A/wKgBZ1oRSX-AFqRYAAfkgb5fMNM58.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/8A/wKgBZ1oRSX-AFqRYAAfkgb5fMNM58.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="266951380" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" target="_blank" class="_j_anchor">
                    <i class="house"></i>北京
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="267002541">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;△&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;李小老烧饼(常营民族家园店)<br />
地址：<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/62068.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="朝阳" target="_blank">朝阳</a>北路民族家园1号内10-11号(近清真寺北墙)<br />
营业时间：&nbsp;周一至周日&nbsp;05:00-18:00<br />
这家店雪花开着车拉了六十个烧饼回去和朋友分食。他家的烧饼就两种，牛肉的“香脆有型”；芝麻的“外酥里韧”，内芯“层层分明”，“丝毫没有发黏粘结”，确实“独到”，配上一碗“香浓”的豆腐脑，也是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>早餐的标配了。<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_266951382" data-seq="266951403" data-pid="266951382" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8002059/266951382.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/8D/wKgBZ1oRSYKALzqfAAqQ9trCOFE24.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/8D/wKgBZ1oRSYKALzqfAAqQ9trCOFE24.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="266951382" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" target="_blank" class="_j_anchor">
                    <i class="house"></i>北京
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="267005839">
            要吃也得赶早儿，李记烧饼物美价廉早已名声在外，东西也是刚出炉的最好吃，好容易来一次不外带点都对不起自个儿您说是不。在这里你还可以点杂碎汤，羊杂汤，油饼，面茶，火烧，炒饼，酱蹄筋……我们是没这个胃，期待您的光临了您㖏~<br />

        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="269509810">
            ❄️雪花说❄️这家清真早餐铺子在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>很多很多年了，也算是老字号，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>人都几十个烧饼这样的买回家当早点，所以我们第一次就买了60个！他家的烧饼不仅用肉实在，连烧饼上的芝麻都能让人回味无穷！而且，他们家的油饼真的超级好吃，我一个女孩子都能吃两个！！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_266951379" data-seq="266951400" data-pid="266951379" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8002059/266951379.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/89/wKgBZ1oRSX6ANkKhAAssVN0CXzs56.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/89/wKgBZ1oRSX6ANkKhAAssVN0CXzs56.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="266951379" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" target="_blank" class="_j_anchor">
                    <i class="house"></i>北京
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="267006798">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;△&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;北新桥卤煮老店&nbsp;<br />
地址：东四北大街141号(近如家北新桥店)<br />
营业时间：&nbsp;周一至周日&nbsp;11:00-14:00&nbsp;17:30-04:00&nbsp;<br />
卤煮的料可“真不少”，大肠、小肠、猪肺、火烧&nbsp;、豆腐，满满当当一大碗，够我们三个人分着吃的了，为了去油腻还点了盘儿拍黄瓜，后来发现多虑了，卤煮吃口一点都不腻。<br />
卤味偏淡，我发现<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>饭馆儿喜欢先把东西做淡，自己去浇“韭菜花、辣椒油、蒜泥、酱豆腐或者醋”，咸淡看自己。晚上十点逛完南锣鼓巷去的，堂里还是上座率90%，可见味道不一般。<br />

        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="269509222">
            ❄️雪花说❄️想尝试吃卤煮真的建议大家选好店，不要轻易选择一家，不然别说不好吃了，闻着都想吐！北新桥卤煮，门框卤煮，小肠陈都是老字号了，可以任意挑一家店去尝试。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_266951378" data-seq="266951399" data-pid="266951378" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8002059/266951378.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/87/wKgBZ1oRSXyABrIUAAbewvar2D408.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/87/wKgBZ1oRSXyABrIUAAbewvar2D408.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="266951378" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" target="_blank" class="_j_anchor">
                    <i class="house"></i>北京
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="267183109">
            <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>当然还有很多想吃的小吃，别的不说，这冰糖包山楂就是地道的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>小吃，虽然全国各地叫法不一，但广为人知的还是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>的“糖葫芦”。驴打滚儿，艾窝窝，奶油炸糕……就是那酸了吧唧的豆汁儿配上焦圈儿都透着这么一股子老<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>儿……<br />

        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="269509141">
            ❄️雪花说❄️冰糖葫芦简直是我的最爱，一到冬天恨不得一天一根，我喜欢吃刚出锅带点微热的糖葫芦。避雷提醒：别买大栅栏稻香村门口10元一串的，那糖葫芦是软的<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/24@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />。<br />
<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>的小吃当然还有很多很多啦，想吃的可以去护国寺小吃吃吃看，每个都点一遍的话也就100多块钱，性价比非常高哦。
        </p>
            <div data-seq="267041167" data-index="2" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <img src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/28/49/wKgBZ1oRi0aARGkkAABMQNUIGfE023.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fh%2F150%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" class="no_word _j_anchor" title="居在北京" alt="居在北京" />
            </div>
    
</div>
